<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Hide</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/E2.css" >
</head>
<body>
    <h1>You chose to hide.</h1>
    <h2>Related rules:</h2>
    <h4>
        <%= hide %>
    </h4>
    <br>
    <h3>
        In this case, you need to roll a 20-side dice. If your roll + Dex modifier is bigger than 10, you hide successfully. Otherwise, you have a 30% chance hurt by the wolf.
    </h3>
    <h4>You can now roll the dice to see whether you hide successfully.</h4>
    <button onclick="rolladice()"> roll your dice </button>
    <p id="num" style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">
        You rolled a <%= playernum %>.
    </p>
    <p id="hide" style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">
        <%= success %>
    </p>
    <p id="wolf" style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">
        The wolf hits you with <%= wolfharm %> points. You have <%= hd %> points left.
    </p>
    <form action="/app/E2/fight/turns" method="get">
        <button type="submit">Next</button>
    <script>
        function rolladice(){
            document.getElementById("wolf").style.color="white";
            document.getElementById("hide").style.color="white";
            document.getElementById("num").style.color="white";
        }
    </script>
    
</body>
</html>